<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>기업 마이페이지 -> 채용공고 관리</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .table th {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="upMenu text-center mb-4">
                <h1>마이페이지</h1>
                <div class="btn-group btn-group-lg">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-dark">프로필 관리</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-dark">채용공고 관리</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-dark">지원 관리</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-dark">로그아웃</button>
                </div>
                <div class="m-3">
                    <h2>채용공고 관리</h2>
                    <table class="table table-bordered" style="width: 100%;">
                        <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th scope="col">번호</th>
                            <th scope="col">지원 공고</th>
                            <th scope="col">지원자 현황</th>
                        </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody id="adTable">
                        <tr>
                            <td>1</td>
                            <td>[카카오모빌리디] 서버(백엔드) 개발자</td>
                            <td>현재 15명</td>
                        </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary">새로운 채용공고 작성하기</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>

</html>
